{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_15", "eventName": "解離重組", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "15-7", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "臨界時刻", "storyInfo": "博士和阿米婭完成了思維共享，並在黑王冠的協助下準備越過“文明的存續”的邊界。阿米婭親眼看到了博士曾經向她講述的童話。卡特斯感染者見到了深空中的神秘精靈。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ceo", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$calm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#1$2", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，我從未嘗試過利用黑王冠來接觸你的思維——", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#1$2"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "不必緊張，阿米婭。;我已經完全向你敞開我的內心和思維。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line15", "option2": "line15"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……好。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#1$2"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她看向了自己的身側，那一束溫柔的白光正輕輕拉著她的手。"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她閉上眼，長舒一口氣。"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“我們一起，阿米婭。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#6$2"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，我也不知道我們這趟旅程通往何處，但我會保護你。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#6$2"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“我也會保護你，阿米婭。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她在“魔王”的注視下，輕輕觸碰著你的額前——"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#3$2"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 3.0, "type": "bg", "from": 0.0, "to": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的記憶和情感正向我流淌過來。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#3$2"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……感覺很奇怪。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#3$2"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明明它們的波動如此平靜溫和，明明記憶的盡頭並不遙遠……", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#3$2"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當初特蕾西婭小姐到底看到了什麼——", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#3$2"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿米婭看到你，看到了凱爾希，看到了自己，還有羅德島上許許多多的人。"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她越走越深，那個記憶的邊界已經觸手可及。“好奇”與“擔憂”致使她幾乎忘記了自己的目的，她想要觸及那道邊界……"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "想要觸及你記憶的起點。切爾諾伯格、石棺，還有那個虛弱地伸出手的你——"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 0.0, "type": "bg", "from": 1.0, "to": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "avg_0_1", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“博士……抓緊我的手！！”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好像還有其他的記憶？為什麼模糊不清？", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "MusicVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_signlntrfrnc", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_signalInterference", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 0.0, "type": "cg", "from": 0.0, "to": 1.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "avg_8_9", "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_signalInterference", "layer": 2.0}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 0.0, "type": "cg", "from": 1.0, "to": 0.0}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "avg_0_1", "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——？！", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是——", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“阿米婭！”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "MusicVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#5$2"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的手抓住了阿米婭。"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "……你迷失了？", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line90"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#7$2"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我、我不知道，這也是我第一次如此深入地接觸他人的思維，這種感覺……很奇異。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#7$2"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "但好在你成功了。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line96"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#8$2"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，博士，我現在能感受到你每一絲細微的情緒。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#8$2"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "我也能感受到你。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line102"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#11$2"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸，你現在很放鬆嘛！", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#11$2"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "有阿米婭在，我並不需要擔心什麼。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line108"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 109, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "接下來，我們應該怎麼做？", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line112"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#8$2"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，拉緊我的手。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#8$2"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "接下來的路，我會保護你走下去的。關於魔王的一切，特蕾西婭小姐在那一天已經全部教給了我。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#8$2"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在那條路的前面，“她”已經在等著我們了。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#8$2"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$desolate_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "……", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "我理解你的理由，但我無法提供，你的請求違背了DWDB-221E的核心邏輯。", "x": 250.0, "y": 300.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 820.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n但我可以提供繞過限制的方法，凱爾希——", "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n“深潛”。", "alignment": "left", "duration": 1.0, "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n可惜連特蕾西婭也無法走到如此遙遠的地方，其中的風險遠遠超過了她所能承受的範圍——", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n你並不奢求從我這裡獲得答案？那為何你如此執著於求助我存取這些於你無益的數據？", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_signlntrfrnc", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_signalInterference", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#1$1", "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“我無法確認是否終有一天，阿米婭會向你提出同樣的問題。但我希望，她能在黑暗中找到我為她照亮的方向。”", "name": "魔王"}, "figure_art": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#1$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凱爾希便是如此回答我，阿米婭。", "name": "魔王"}, "figure_art": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#1$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……請問您能為我們調出凱爾希醫生的所有存取記錄嗎？", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然。", "name": "魔王"}, "figure_art": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#1$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她每一次的疑惑、每一次的堅持，還有每一次的失落離去，我將無一保留地展示給你們。", "name": "魔王"}, "figure_art": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#1$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿米婭，你也曾深入過“文明的存續”，但這一次，你所尋找的東西遠在邊際之外。", "name": "魔王"}, "figure_art": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#1$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是泰拉生命暫時無法踏足的領域，但或許你有機會接觸那些不屬於你們的知識。", "name": "魔王"}, "figure_art": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#1$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為你的同行者——Dr.{@nickname}。", "name": "魔王"}, "figure_art": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#1$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "……我？", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line152"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你很快便會知曉我的意思，Dr.{@nickname}。", "name": "魔王"}, "figure_art": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#1$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "隨我來吧，阿米婭，來到——", "name": "魔王"}, "figure_art": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#1$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "60_g6_crownboundary", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.3, "yScale": 1.3, "x": 60.0}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "backgroundTween", "attributes": {"duration": 30.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“文明奇點”。"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "純白巨型長廊環繞著中央那不可捉摸的點——“奇點”。"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "龐雜的資訊流不斷從奇點中溢出，能夠被你們所捕獲的資訊皆是足以被你們理解的知識。"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿米婭看不到來時的路。但要是沿著長廊繼續走下去，在浪費了難以估量的時間後，阿米婭終將回到原點。"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "60_g6_crownboundary", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你發現了，阿米婭。", "name": "魔王"}, "figure_art": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#1$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "文明發展的停滯並非意味著原地踏步，時間依舊會在線性的軌跡上不可逆轉地向前推進。", "name": "魔王"}, "figure_art": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#1$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但生命所創造的和所發現的一切卻只會陷入無法脫離的循環。", "name": "魔王"}, "figure_art": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#1$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "數學、物理、哲學、神學等各種理論和實踐都無法再創造希望。", "name": "魔王"}, "figure_art": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#1$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "向上的螺旋已經失效，生命將在迷失方向的道路上空耗他們的未來。", "name": "魔王"}, "figure_art": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#1$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以……這裡就已經是邊界？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#1$2"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是泰拉目前所能觸碰的知識邊界。它既是限制，也是保護。", "name": "魔王"}, "figure_art": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#1$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "保護？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#1$2"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "某種思維認知的保護……", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line189"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#7$2"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "思維認知？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#7$2"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "就像我們沒辦法強迫小沙地獸計算洋流的規律？", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line195"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "哪怕我們能給出所有的數據和公式……", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line198"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "硬來依舊會傷害牠們的小腦瓜。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line202"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的直覺很敏銳，博士，但並非完全準確。", "name": "魔王"}, "figure_art": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#1$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "DWDB-221E會啟迪生命穩步走向未來，而非簡單將未來的碎片展現於求索者的眼前，導致違背自然規律與倫理的演化飛躍。", "name": "魔王"}, "figure_art": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#7$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿米婭，知識是不可逆轉的。瞥見過真實天空的理想家將不再甘願蒙昧地安眠於大地。", "name": "魔王"}, "figure_art": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#7$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而超越文明本身思維認知極限的資訊，只會變成誘惑他們忽視現實，走向毀滅陷阱的毒藥，繼而將他們的文明帶入深淵。", "name": "魔王"}, "figure_art": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#7$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "於是，邊界誕生了。", "name": "魔王"}, "figure_art": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#7$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但為什麼邊界的構成……像是某種龐大的資料伺服器組成的監牢？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#1$2"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它以你所能接受的形態出現，一如DWDB-221E在物質界以一頂黑色冠冕的形態陪伴著你。", "name": "魔王"}, "figure_art": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#7$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對渺小的螻蟻而言，邊界可以是一條首尾相連的湍急河流，永遠無法匯入大海。", "name": "魔王"}, "figure_art": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#7$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而對壽命以萬億年計量的天體而言，邊界亦可以是伴隨其一生的引力場，不可捉摸，不可逃脫。", "name": "魔王"}, "figure_art": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#7$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你走向了與虛空一步之遙的斷面，遙遠中心處的“奇點”在吸引著你。"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "資訊如波浪般輕輕地從你身旁掠過，卻足以讓你一瞥許多新奇的場景。"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是屬於你過去的浮光掠影——你失去後又遺忘的生活。"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個“陌生時代”的幻影。"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "……", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line225"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#6$2"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，小心！", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#6$2"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿米婭緊張地拉住了你的手。"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#6$2"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們沒辦法確認從邊界墜下會發生什麼——", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#6$2"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#5$2"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些是……你看到的……？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#5$2"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "……你我思維相通……;……你能看到我所看到的……", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line237", "option2": "line237"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#5$2"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——“源石蟲的卵鞘”、“穿過星星之間的獨木橋”——", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#5$2"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#9$2"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……所有那些故事都是真實存在的。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#9$2"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "“源石蟲的卵鞘”？;“穿過星星之間的獨木橋”？", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line245", "option2": "line245"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#1$2"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#8$2"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在很小很小的時候，我遇到了一個很在意的人。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#8$2"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個人明明自己也脆弱得不行，卻一定要固執地背著我跨過滿是源石碎屑的小徑。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#8$2"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在我發燒昏昏沉沉，但又害怕惡夢不敢睡覺的時候，那個人也會不厭其煩地跟我講那些我從未聽過的故事。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#8$2"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在逼仄黑暗的礦洞裡，那個人也會毫不猶豫地砸碎自己好不容易找到的礦石樣本——", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#8$2"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後把那些發光的小石頭嵌在四周的岩壁上，為我講述星星，還有坐落在雲天之上的樂園的故事。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#8$2"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "……", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line257"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#8$2"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，願意聽聽那個人跟我講的故事嗎？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#8$2"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "……;當然。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line263", "option2": "line263"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有一個人，總是獨自駕駛著像是源石蟲卵鞘的神奇載具穿過星星之間的獨木橋。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#1$2"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在最為幽靜的夜晚，也有引路人從上了年紀的星星那裡借來發光的雲朵，造出圓圓的鏡子照亮前路。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#1$2"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而在獨木橋的另一頭，尖塔在大氣潮汐中若隱若現，還有戴在星星額頭上的花環。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#1$2"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當降落在花環上時，會發現那裡是一座很大很大的遊樂場，而可愛的好孩子們會聚集在那裡肆意玩耍。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#1$2"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但駕駛載具的人卻很難停下……", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#1$2"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那人會換到一艘最神奇的載具裡，駕駛著它駛過漫長的歲月……", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#1$2"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而歲月的盡頭，卻空無一人。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#1$2"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#2$2"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只剩自己。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#2$2"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "那是……我？;為你講故事的人……是我？", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line277", "option2": "line277"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿米婭緊緊地握住了你的手。"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#1$2"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "由於感染的緣故，那時我很難記住很多的東西，我也無法理解故事裡的很多東西。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#1$2"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我會努力去想，盡全力去記住你講過的每一個故事。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#1$2"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為那是屬於我的故事，是你送給我的故事。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#1$2"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我不想忘記。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#1$2"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#8$2"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，沒想到今天我終於可以把這些你送我的禮物再分享給你。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#8$2"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這一次，我們已經共同親眼見證。於我，於你，都重新認識了那段逝去的生活。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#8$2"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "謝謝你，阿米婭……", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line291"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 292, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#8$2"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，你會嚮往那樣的生活嗎？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#8$2"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "嚮往。;不嚮往。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line297", "option2": ""}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 298, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#8$2"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也難怪。和博士一樣，第一次想到那些奇妙的生活時，我也嚮往過。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#8$2"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那樣的生活是我無論如何也沒辦法真正觸碰的。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#8$2"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會忍不住偷偷和特蕾西婭小姐分享，我們會用許多奇怪的想像增添更多的細節——", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#8$2"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直到它變得面目全非，變得越來越遙不可及……", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#8$2"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而現在親眼瞥見一點點之後，我反而覺得自己和你過去的生活不再那麼遙遠了。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#8$2"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Dr.{@nickname}，你相信我們的這片大地終有一天也會如那樣美好嗎？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#8$2"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "我相信。;會有那麼一天的。;也許會更好……", "values": "1;1;1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line308"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;1;1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 309, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#8$2"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，我們會見到。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#8$2"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "羅德島會見到的。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#8$2"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "2"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#7$2"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "並不嚮往？奇怪，那樣的生活的確很美好不是嗎？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#7$2"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有礦石病的痛苦、沒有紛爭與戰亂，孩子們能盡情地享受快樂……", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#1$2"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "或許只是不願意將殘酷的另一面分享給你。;我始終堅信生活的背面永遠存在，阿米婭。", "values": "2;2"}, "targetLine": {}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "2;2"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#3$2"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許吧。快樂背後的殘酷、痛苦背後的喜悅，我們的確都已體驗過。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#3$2"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，我也偷偷向特蕾西婭小姐分享過那些奇妙的故事，她同樣為此驚訝。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#1$2"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她一直渴望著卡茲戴爾……不，是渴望著這片大地的每個人都有機會體驗那樣的生活。也因此她不斷努力著。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#1$2"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#8$2"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們可不能落後啊，博士。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#8$2"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許終有一天，羅德島也能在這片大地上見證那樣的生活。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#8$2"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "……", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "我們接下來該怎麼做？", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“深潛”。", "name": "魔王"}, "figure_art": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#1$1"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "DWDB-221E所儲存的完整數據會經由奇點解碼並輸出合理且適當的資訊。", "name": "魔王"}, "figure_art": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#1$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "僅靠阿米婭無法突破其核心邏輯的限制。", "name": "魔王"}, "figure_art": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#1$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "……我是特例？", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "尚未可知，但的確存在這樣的可能性。", "name": "魔王"}, "figure_art": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#1$1"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但那些資訊，我們如何接近呢？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#1$2"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，阿米婭，對此我並無更加有效的資料。", "name": "魔王"}, "figure_art": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#10$1"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我能夠不斷搜尋凱爾希所留下的線索，讓可能對你們有用的資訊在排序上更容易被找到。", "name": "魔王"}, "figure_art": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#10$1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "也許能搭建一座橋？", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "橋？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#1$2"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "通向奇點的橋。;通向知識的橋。;凱爾希不是已經為我們指引了前路嗎？", "values": "1;2;3"}, "targetLine": {}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2;3"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "曾有人這麼做過嗎？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#1$2"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "記錄中並無先例。", "name": "魔王"}, "figure_art": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#7$1"}, {"id": 366, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#6$2"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……無論如何，值得一試。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#6$2"}, {"id": 368, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這其中的風險你們必須知曉，越靠近奇點，資訊的密度會越高，你們甚至極有可能體驗到資訊的質量。", "name": "魔王"}, "figure_art": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#10$1"}, {"id": 370, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#5$2"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "資訊存在質量？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#5$2"}, {"id": 372, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這裡，它存在。", "name": "魔王"}, "figure_art": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#10$1"}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "且未完全篩選的資訊有機率如洪流般摧毀你們的思維。", "name": "魔王"}, "figure_art": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#10$1"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而思維湮滅意味著……", "name": "魔王"}, "figure_art": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#3$1"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "死亡。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "60_g2_rhodeslivingroom_bc", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$saferoom_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（未知語言）旅者，我只是在目睹又一次毀滅的發生罷了。", "name": "自內心響起的聲音"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（未知語言）希爾達，這是你的名字吧？", "name": "自內心響起的聲音"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在叫我的名字？", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#1$1"}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我無法理解你的語言。而且，你是怎麼知道——", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#1$1"}, {"id": 397, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡特斯透過舷窗看到那個深空中的身影慢慢向自己所在的艦船靠近，繼而消失在了視野之外。"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "屈光者，請問那是誰？", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#1$1"}, {"id": 401, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1725_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "action": "jump", "posto": "0,0", "power": 50.0, "times": 1.0, "duration": 0.8}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（激烈的歌聲）♪——♪——♪——", "name": "屈光者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1725_1#1$1"}, {"id": 406, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——您怎麼了？！", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#9$1"}, {"id": 408, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1725_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們很少有人喜歡她！", "name": "屈光者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1725_1#1$1"}, {"id": 410, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，旅者，我實在無法容忍自己與她共處一室。", "name": "屈光者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1725_1#1$1"}, {"id": 411, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的其他朋友要是看到了，也會因為這個唾棄我。", "name": "屈光者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1725_1#1$1"}, {"id": 412, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-200,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當困惑的卡特斯回過神來時，整間艙室中除了她已經空無一人。在預感到某個不受歡迎的人到來之前，所有人都已經提前離開了。"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1720_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cosmicelfvoice"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後卡特斯看到了。"}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1720_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不必驚訝，我學習過透過遠距離共振進行交流的技巧。", "name": "神秘的精靈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1720_1#2$1"}, {"id": 427, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至少，在毀滅那個奇特的種族之前，我保留下了他們進化出的獨特語言模式。", "name": "神秘的精靈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1720_1#2$1"}, {"id": 428, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……毀、毀滅？", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#1$1"}, {"id": 430, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1720_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（嘆氣）", "name": "神秘的精靈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1720_1#1$1"}, {"id": 432, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "新來的客人，你也對毀滅的行為不齒？", "name": "神秘的精靈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1720_1#1$1"}, {"id": 433, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……並不清楚發生了什麼。", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#4$1"}, {"id": 435, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1720_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "並不複雜，我們的族群曾經以噬星為生。其他人所厭惡的，無非是我們賴以生存的本能而已。", "name": "神秘的精靈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1720_1#1$1"}, {"id": 437, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，如今我們的過往都只是流傳於旁人口中的恐怖奇談罷了。", "name": "神秘的精靈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1720_1#1$1"}, {"id": 438, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的族群幾近滅絕，恐怕我已經是最後一人。", "name": "神秘的精靈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1720_1#1$1"}, {"id": 439, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵，我們以毀滅為生，最終當真正的毀滅降臨於我們的面前時，我們卻無能為力……", "name": "神秘的精靈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1720_1#1$1"}, {"id": 440, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "自那以後，作為苟活者，我已經在幾位天才的幫助下改變了攝入生存必要能量的方式——", "name": "神秘的精靈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1720_1#1$1"}, {"id": 441, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽起來……您也正試著融入另一種生活。", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#1$1"}, {"id": 443, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以剛剛您在深空中注視著那顆死去的星球，也是在緬懷您所經歷的毀滅？", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#1$1"}, {"id": 444, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1720_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 445, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "緬懷？", "name": "神秘的精靈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1720_1#1$1"}, {"id": 446, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，並非如此。", "name": "神秘的精靈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1720_1#1$1"}, {"id": 447, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1720_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 448, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡的每個人都坦然且樂觀地接受毀滅追上我們。", "name": "神秘的精靈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1720_1#3$1"}, {"id": 449, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 450, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——？！", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#10$1"}, {"id": 451, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 452, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 453, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 454, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 455, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 456, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 457, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": false}